text: Djoao Lobles (born 14 January 2001) is a Dutch track and field athlete who is specalized in the 800 metres. Lobles represents Netherlands at international competitions. He became national champion at the 2020 Dutch Athletics Championships and 2020 Dutch Indoor Athletics Championships. He repeated both and is as of 2022 two times national indoor champion and two times national outdoor champion. He competed at the 2022 European Athletics Championships in the 800 metres event. ==References== Category:2001 births Category:Dutch athletes Category:Living people
